ms-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">□</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">□</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span></span></span></span> )，并为无需 Lob 定理的基于 Lobian 握手的合作提供了基础。</p><p>众所周知，洛布定理<a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/oBDTMnEzptBidvmw7/probabilistic-loeb-theorem">在逻辑不确定性的反思理论中不成立</a>。然而，已经提出了<a href="https://www.alignmentforum.org/posts/ZWhJcHPmRaXAPAK5k/probabilistic-payor-lemma">概率支付引理的证明</a>，它修改了必要的推理规则：</p><ul><li><strong>必要性：</strong> <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\vdash x \implies \vdash \Box_p \, x,"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⊢</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.278em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⟹</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.278em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⊢</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">□</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span></span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.167em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">X</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">，</span></span></span></span></span></span></li><li><strong>弱分布性：</strong> <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\vdash x \to y \implies \vdash \Box_p \, x \to \Box_p \, y."><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⊢</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">→</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.278em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⟹</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.278em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⊢</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">□</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span></span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.167em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">→</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">□</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span></span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.167em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em; padding-right: 0.006em;">y</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">。</span></span></span></span></span></span>这里我们将<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Box_p"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">□</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>视为一个运算符，如果<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="x"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span></span></span></span>的内部可信度大于<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="p"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span></span></span></span></span> ，则返回 True，否则返回 False。 （形式主义传入）。</li></ul><p>那么问题是：这些推理规则是否存在一致的形式主义？答案是肯定的，这是由<a href="http://intelligence.org/files/DefinabilityTruthDraft.pdf">Christiano 2012</a>提供的。</p><h1>设置</h1><p>(Regurgitation and rewording of the relevant parts of the <a href="http://intelligence.org/files/DefinabilityTruthDraft.pdf">Definability of Truth</a> )</p><p>令<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="L"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L</span></span></span></span></span></span>为某种语言， <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="T"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.12em;">T</span></span></span></span></span></span>为该语言的理论。假设<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="L"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">L</span></span></span></span></span></span>足够强大，可以接受哥德尔编码，并且它包含与有理数<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mathbb{Q}."><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-texatom"><span class="mjx-mrow"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span></span></span>相对应的项<span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-T